additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Bolognese sauce (46%) (water, beef (8%), tomato (tomato, tomato juice, acidity regulator (330), tomato paste, onions, capsicum, carrots, celery, flavour (malt extract (wheat, barley), natural flavours, balsamic vinegar, colours (caramel iv, carotene), sugar, vegetable oil (olive, sunflower, soybean), spice, spice extract), thickener (1422), flour (wheat), salt, canola oil, herbs), cooked pasta (32%) (wheat flour, water), cheese sauce (21%) (cheese (cream, milk, salt, milk solids, cultures, enzymes), water, milk solids, thickener (1422), flavour, stabilisers (415, 466), emulsifier (331), acidity regulator (451), food acid (270), yeast extract (wheat, barley), natural colours (carotene, turmeric)), parmesan crumb (1%) (breadcrumbs (wheat), parmesan cheese, paprika, parsley).

description: A traditional-style Lasagne layered with beef bolognese, topped with a rich tasty cheese sauce, finished with a Parmesan crumb.
name: Red Box Tray Lasagna
